
Directory $PDAZX/Source/Formats/Storage

Yeah--I have a few _slight_ issues with how everybody doing GBA and NDS 
development seem to suggest using FAT16 or FAT32. Those are horrible file 
systems. Which is part of why I kind of want to add support for JFS and XFS 
into what we can use here.

Mostly as this is not only suppose to be something for Modding Pokemon games, 
but I kind of want this system to be able to make a Pokemon game n,n
